      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong>&nbsp;<em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 136</em></p>\n<p><strong>Aura</strong>&nbsp;faint enchantment&nbsp;<strong>CL</strong>&nbsp;5th</p>\n<p><strong>Slot</strong>&nbsp;weapon quality;&nbsp;<strong>Price</strong>&nbsp;+1 bonus;&nbsp;<strong>Weight</strong>&nbsp;-</p>\n<h3 class=\"framing\"><img style=\"margin: 3px 3px 0px 3px;\" title=\"PFS Legal\" src=\"https://www.aonprd.com/images/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" /><strong>Description</strong></h3>\n<p>This ability can only be placed on a melee weapon. When the wielder of a benevolent weapon uses the aid another action to grant an ally a bonus on attack rolls, he increases the aid another bonus by the enhancement bonus of the weapon.</p>\n<h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong>&nbsp;Craft Magic Arms and Armor,&nbsp;<em>aid</em>;&nbsp;<strong>Price</strong>&nbsp;-</p>",
